===message:I really do not believe the New Deal was intended to 'end the depression totally', rather than as much as it was to help the starved.  The New Deal was to put Americans back to work to be able to support their family on the basic needs of life, i.e. food, clothing, and medical.  It did however save the people, saved the people from death, so in a way, it did save the country, the Americans that made up our country.
